        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a cultivated specimen of <hi rend="italic">Myosotis</hi> (first generation) grown from seed sent by JSH. Asks for a tuft of flower.</p> 
            <p>Hopes JSH will publish a book on teaching botany, because he has no idea how to begin with his children.</p>
